{"tid":1641612,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"警員警署偷勞力士案","createTime":"2019-10-09T11:44:44.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-09T12:29:53.000Z","uid":321002,"like":15,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"f5afad3bd136066e3cc79974d92705c47138d709","tid":1641612,"uid":321002,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T11:44:44.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/article/384093\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2Farticle%2F384093&d=B%2BAVUFxUUUF%2FouYpVm7lNtLD3cQOkzCKckuFp%2FmPVdU%3D&h=0da82d79\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/article/384093</a><br />\n<br />\n警員警署偷勞力士案　物主直斥離譜對警隊失信心　要求其錶鎖夾萬<br />\n<br />\n男警在警署內涉以「假勞」，換走市民拾到一隻價值42.5萬的地通拿系列「真勞」案，男警今（9日）在區域法院被裁定盜竊罪成，案件押後至11月22日判刑。失物的主人接受傳媒訪問時稱，市民因信任警方，才會把拾到的財物交去警署，惟這次「偷龍轉鳳」事件離譜，他認為涉案警員做法「好錯」，動搖市民對警方的信心，他更因而一直取不回失錶，惟有要求警方要將其錶放入夾萬保管。<br />\n<br />\n吊你，警察係唔會做犯法事<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"44765dd9258d4ee0e9d9d9a562896eb776c2f96c","tid":1641612,"uid":224860,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T11:47:00.000Z","msg":"屌 一定要推"},{"pid":"f3ec29720265b10e644750400c9e6a2bb3f33ddc","tid":1641612,"uid":219128,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T11:47:55.000Z","msg":"香港警察，污糟邋遢。"},{"pid":"77614871ab892575319026d3033fac946dcedaf4","tid":1641612,"uid":224860,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T11:48:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/EY5xkSi.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FEY5xkSi.png&h=0631d3c5&s={SIZE}\" /> <strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">偷嘢個死黑警叫周合駿</span></span></strong> 有無人識佢？"},{"pid":"a07ed0f251a269ad26854515123d8fdd2d81c250","tid":1641612,"uid":321002,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyT